squidS2140eMethods of "Random" that return floating point values should not be used in random integer generation"MAJOR*java2S2140:Õ<p>There is no need to multiply the output of <code>Random</code>'s <code>nextDouble</code> method to get a random integer. Use the <code>nextInt</code> method instead.</p>
