abapS1066,Collapsible "IF" statements should be merged"MAJOR*abap:«<p>Merging collapsible <code>if</code> statements increases the code's readability.</p>

<h2>Noncompliant Code Example</h2>

<pre>
IF something.
  IF somethingElse.
    WRITE / 'hello'.
  ENDIF.
ENDIF.
</pre>

