abapS1238HSubroutine parameters should be passed by reference rather than by value"MAJOR*abap:∞<p>Passing parameters by reference instead of by value avoids the overhead of making a copy. Passing arguments via copy should only be done when it is technically mandated, as it is for example with RFC function modules.</p>
<h2>Compliant Solution</h2>

<pre>
PERFORM subr CHANGING a1 a2 a3 a4 a5.
