abap:S1491Œ
abapS1491*Obsolete "REFRESH itab" should not be used"MAJOR*abap:Ö<p>This statement deletes all rows of an internal table itab. This <code>REFRESH</code> statement is deprecated and usage should be avoided.</p>
<h2>Noncompliant Code Example</h2>

<pre>
REFRESH itab.
