abap:S1498¨
abapS1498F"LIKE" operator should be used very carefully in SQL "WHERE" condition"MAJOR*abap:«<p>Using the <code>LIKE</code> operator in SQL <code>WHERE</code> conditions can highly impact the performance of the request. The use of this operator should be strongly indicated.</p>
<h2>Noncompliant Code Example</h2>

<pre>
