abap:S1655ö
abapS16552"FORM... ENDFORM" and "PERFORM" should not be used"MAJOR*abap:…<p>Procedural development in general, and <code>FORM... ENDFORM</code>, and <code>PERFORM</code> specifically, have been been classified as obsolete by SAP and should be avoided. Classes and methods should be used for all new development.</p>
<h2>Noncompliant Code Example</h2>

<pre>
FORM fill_table USING    wa   TYPE any 
                CHANGING ptab TYPE INDEX TABLE. 
  APPEND wa TO ptab. 
ENDFORM. 
* ...
PERFORM fill_table IN PROGRAM my_prog.
</pre>
