abap:S1669ü
abapS1669-Keywords should not be used as variable names"MAJOR*abap:”<p>Using keywords as variable names may yield incomprehensible code, and should be avoided.</p>
<h2>Noncompliant Code Example</h2>

<pre>
DATA:  wa_struct TYPE struct,
       name       TYPE string,
       dob          TYPE string,
       aliases     TYPE string,    " ALIASES is a keyword
</pre>
<h2>Compliant Solution</h2>

<pre>
DATA:  wa_struct TYPE struct,
       name         TYPE string,
       dob            TYPE string,
       alt_names  TYPE string,
</pre>
