cS34916Redundant pointer operator sequences should be removed"CRITICAL*c2S3491:¢<p>By contract, chaining the 'Address of' operator <code>&amp;</code> with the 'Indirection' operator <code>*</code> results in a return to the initial value. Thus, such combinations are confusing at best, and bugs at worst.</p>

