cobol.SQL.CursorDeclaredInsideProcedureDivisionCheck;"CURSORs" should not be declared inside procedure divisions"MINOR*cobol2.SQL.CursorDeclaredInsideProcedureDivisionCheck:d<p>It is a bad practice to declare a cursor inside a procedure division, so you should avoid it.</p>
