cobol*SQL.CursorDeclaredWithNoOrderByClauseCheck*"ORDER BY" should be specified for cursors"MAJOR*cobol2*SQL.CursorDeclaredWithNoOrderByClauseCheck:ñ<p>When performing cursor processing, the ORDER BY clause not only helps to process the cursor, but it also it insures reproducibility at runtime.</p>
