cppS3252D"static" base class members should not be accessed via derived types"MAJOR*cpp2S3252:<p>In the interest of code clarity, <code>static</code> members of a <code>base</code> class should never be accessed using a derived type's name. Doing so is confusing and could create the illusion that two different static members exist.</p>

