cppS966CMacros used in preprocessor directives should be defined before use"MAJOR*cpp2S966:—	<p>
  An attempt to use an undefined identifier may elicit a warning from the preprocessor.
  Or it may not; the preprocessor may simply assume that the undefined token has a value of 0.
