cssselector-naming-convention+Selectors should follow a naming convention"MINOR*css:À<p>Shared coding conventions allow teams to collaborate efficiently. This rule checks that all selector names match a
    provided regular expression.</p>
<p>The default regular expression only allows lowercase letters, digits and hyphens. Uppercase letters are not allowed
