fxcop-vbnet%ReviewDeclarativeSecurityOnValueTypes2CA2108: Review declarative security on value types"MAJOR*vbnet2CA2108:…<h2>Cause</h2>
<p>
            A public or protected value type is secured by a <code>Data and Modeling in the .NET Framework</code> or Link Demands.
