</p>
<h2>How Cyclomatic Complexity is Calculated</h2>
<p>
            The cyclomatic complexity is calculated by adding 1 to the following:
            <ul>
              <li>
                Number of branches (such as <code>if</code>, <code>while</code>, and <code>do</code>)
