i = a + b;
</pre>
<h2>Exceptions</h2>

<p>Use of comma operator is tolerated in initialization and increment expressions of <code>for</code> loops.</p>
<pre>
for(i = 0, j = 5; i &lt; 6; i++, j++) { ... }
</pre>
<h2>See</h2>

