objcS876;Unary minus should not be applied to an unsigned expression"MAJOR*objc2S876:ÿ<p>
  Applying the unary minus operator to an unsigned variable or expression will always yield another unsigned expression.
  More plainly, in some cases the operation itself is meaningless, and in some other cases the result will be unexpected.
  In all cases it is bad practice. Therefore the unary minus operator should not be applied to unsigned variables or expressions.
</p>

