objcS989<"atof", "atoi" and "atol" from <stdlib.h> should not be used"MAJOR*objc2S989:Î<p>
  <code>&lt;stdlib.h&gt;</code>'s <code>atof</code>, <code>atoi</code>, and <code>atol</code> functions, which convert strings to numbers,
  have undefined behavior when the strings cannot be converted, and should therefore be avoided.
