phpS11514"switch case" clauses should not have too many lines"MAJOR*php:ˆ<p>The <code>switch</code> statement should be used only to clearly define some new branches in the control flow. As soon as a <code>case</code> clause contains too many statements this highly decreases the readability of the overall control flow statement. In such case, the content of <code>case</code> clause should be extracted in a dedicated function</p>

