phpS2007@Functions and variables should not be defined outside of classes"MAJOR*php:˘	<p>Shared coding conventions allow teams to collaborate efficiently. Defining and using global variables and global functions, when the convention dictates OOP can be confusing and difficult to use properly for multiple reasons:</p>
