    <li><a href="https://docs.puppetlabs.com/puppet/3.8/reference/modules_fundamentals.html#module-layout">See Puppet
        Labs Puppet Module Fundamentals Guide</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://docs.puppetlabs.com/guides/style_guide.html#separate-files">See Puppet Labs Puppet Language
