swiftS3083HPrecedence and associativity of standard operators should not be changed"CRITICAL*swift:±<p>It is acceptable to override standard operators to provide appropriate behaviors for your classes. But it is not appropriate to change those operators' associativity or precedence from the standard. Doing so will inevitably lead to misuse and mistakes for users of the class.</p>
